{"tid":2000866,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱駱惠寧違《基本法》22條　「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅提覆核","createTime":"2020-05-04T06:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T08:10:16.000Z","uid":241764,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b0771f2e329cceed6308a8e7c0559c71977fbe7d","tid":2000866,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"中聯辦早前發聲明指出，港澳辦和中聯辦不是《基本法》第22條所指的「中央人民政府所屬各部門」，故有權就立法會事務等發聲和行使監督權。「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅今（4日）在高等法院申請司法覆核，要求法庭阻止中聯辦主任駱惠寧再發表違反《基本法》第22條的言論。<br />\n<br />\n申請人為郭卓堅，答辯人為中聯辦主任駱惠寧。申請書指出，駱惠寧就公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗主持內會會議的行為發表公開言論，要求法庭頒令駱惠寧違反《基本法》第22條，以及阻止駱惠寧日後再發表相關言論。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅在庭外表示，中聯辦的角色非「太上皇」，批評中聯辦對立法會事宜「指手劃腳」的行為違反《基本法》。"},{"pid":"242b14d0049ceeaedf489bf414076c9f2fafde5c","tid":2000866,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"588f58cdcd0392d9d2c71592207c2cea7c1f5a86","tid":2000866,"uid":46746,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"推 識玩 雖然法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0440d8fb1daefe5aac1189ccc76287cd8cc5e5","tid":2000866,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"手足好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e66acdcc0e43726ec423463c5996c05ba4b161fb","tid":2000866,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:54:11.000Z","msg":"留名睇釋法"},{"pid":"bf692c673b77fb458a1ba4b89a4ba5cd3055ee3a","tid":2000866,"uid":246828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"明知不可為而為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持郭生"},{"pid":"bb53021be56ceb448e3bd4e1eae42b0a5f766b7f","tid":2000866,"uid":237425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"老而彌堅猛將手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4b952970b9ce7f18f67871dfd834d507b732cc","tid":2000866,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"99%唔受理"},{"pid":"88fb056540484042667115da29d2df6d678f9fcc","tid":2000866,"uid":237425,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"588f58cdcd0392d9d2c71592207c2cea7c1f5a86","tid":2000866,"uid":46746,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"推 識玩 雖然法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"入一入紙已經係一單新聞<br />\n又多左人討論有NOISE<br />\n一陣法院唔小心講錯左真話出黎就好多野玩"},{"pid":"f4c28193b117c86e86d6cfaee780c192568037f4","tid":2000866,"uid":277302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep